title: Lombardi’s Conference Championship Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 389)
description:
The "No-Call in NOLA” allows the Rams to slip by the Saints, and the Patriots outlast the Chiefs for another trip to the Super Bowl.


Hosts: Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier
